{"id": "1000324", "question": "ARIMA模型中的三个参数(p, d, q)都是什么意思?", "description": "<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-10\"><p>这三个数分别有什么具体的含义？能举例说明就更好了！谢谢！</p></div>", "viewer": 23991, "tags": ["统计/机器学习", "时间序列"], "answers": [{"lvl1_answer": "<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-10 p-r\"><p>ARIMA(p,d,q)模型中</p><p>p是自回归(AR)的项数，用来获取自变量</p><p>d是差分(I)的系数，为了使时间序列平稳</p><p>q是移动平均(MA)的项数，为了使其光滑</p><p><br/></p><p>举个例子，假如原来的时间序列是</p><p>T <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>Y</p><p>1<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>20</p><p>2 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>22</p><p>3 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>25</p><p>4 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>30</p><p>5 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>40</p><p>6<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>50</p><p>7 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>65</p><p>8 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>88</p><p>9 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>112</p><p>10<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>120</p><p>11 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>115</p><p>12 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>？</p><p><br/></p><p>我们先添加自回归项。自回归的意思就是用之前的p个数值当作自变量。若p=2，</p><p>T <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>Y<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>X_1<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>X_2</p><p>1<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>20<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>\\<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>\\</p><p>2 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>22<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>20<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>\\<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span></p><p>3 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>25<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>22<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>20</p><p>4 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>30<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>25<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>22</p><p>5 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>40<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>30<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>25</p><p>6<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>50<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>40<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>30</p><p>7 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>65<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>50<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>40</p><p>8 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>88<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>65<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>50</p><p>9 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>112<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>88<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>65</p><p>10<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>120<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>112<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>88</p><p>11 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>115<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>120<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>112</p><p>12 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>？<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>115<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>120</p><p><br/></p><p>下面我们对自变量和应变量做差分。差分的意思就是后一行减前一行。d=1的意思，我们做一次差分。</p><p>T <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>Y<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>X_1<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>X_2</p><p>1<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>20*<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>\\<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>\\</p><p>2 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>2<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>\\<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>\\<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span></p><p>3 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>3<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>2<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>\\</p><p>4 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>5<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>3<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>2</p><p>5 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>10<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>5<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>3</p><p>6<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>10<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>10<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>5</p><p>7 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>15<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>10<span class=\