tyle=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>\\</p><p>4 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>2<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>1<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>\\</p><p>5 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>5<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>2<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>1</p><p>6<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>0<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>5<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>2</p><p>7 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>5<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>0<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>5</p><p>8 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>8<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>5<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>0</p><p>9 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>1<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>8<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>5</p><p>10<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>-16<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>1<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>8</p><p>11 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>-13<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>-16<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>1</p><p>12 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>？<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>-13<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>-16</p><p><br/></p><p>下面再对每一列取移动平均数。q是移动平均的项数，意思每一行被自身和自身之前的q-1行的平均数取代。例如q=2，</p><p>T <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>Y<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>X_1<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>X_2</p><p>1<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>\\<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>\\<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>\\</p><p>2 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>\\<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>\\<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>\\<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span></p><p>3 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>\\<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>\\<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>\\</p><p>4 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>1.5<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>\\<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>\\</p><p>5 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>3.5<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>1.5<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>\\</p><p>6<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>2.5<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>3.5<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>1.5</p><p>7 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>2.5<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>2.5<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>3.5</p><p>8 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>6.5<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>2.5<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>2.5</p><p>9 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>4.5<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>6.5<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>2.5</p><p>10<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>-7.5    <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>4.5<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>6.5</p><p>11 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>-14.5<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>-7.5    <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>4.5</p><p>12 <span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>？<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>-14.5<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>-7.5</p><p><br/></p><p>下面就是提取出有数据的6到11行，把X_1, X_2当成自变量，Y当成应变量，用线性回归来预测第12行。最后记得把预测出来的结果用逆差分还原回去。</p></div>", "lvl2_answer": ["d是怎么选的？怎么判断进行了d次差分之后已经平稳了呢？", "请问在做差分的过程中，会损失信息吗"]}]}